# AAC model manifest -- SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for model names.
#
# Consumed by:
#   scripts/linux/fetch-models.sh          (ComfyUI image models, Linux/WSL/macOS)
#   scripts/linux/fetch-ollama-models.sh   (Ollama LLM names, Linux/WSL/macOS)
#   scripts/windows/Fetch-ComfyUIModels.ps1 (ComfyUI image models, Windows-native)
#   run.ps1                                 (Ollama model verification, Windows)
#   core/tests/test_model_name_consistency.py (locks names == env == workflows)
#
# Pipe-delimited:  kind|subdir|name|size_bytes|url
#   kind = comfyui | ollama
#   '-'  = not applicable (ollama: no subdir/size/url, pulled by name)
#
# The ComfyUI names MUST match COMFYUI_CHECKPOINT_NAME / COMFYUI_REFINER_CHECKPOINT_NAME /
# COMFYUI_UPSCALE_MODEL_NAME and the ckpt_name/model_name baked in the workflow JSONs.
